Nicole Berger https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicole_Berger 0 Nicole Elizabeth Berger (born November 27, 2003) is an American actress, model, and pianist from Palm Beach, Florida and New York City. She has starred in the films All At Once (2016) and The Longest Week (2014).
